he%20Kashmir%20issue%20at%20global%20forums.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECommon%20enemy%2C%20shared%20victimhood%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20here%20that%20a%20key%20bridge%20in%20the%20Hindutva-Zionist%20relationship%20becomes%20visible%3A%20a%20common%20cultural%20enemy.%20The%20Israeli%20state%E2%80%99s%20very%20founding%20was%20based%20on%20a%20direct%20military%20confrontation%20with%20Arab%20Muslim%20powers%20and%20displacement%20of%20Arab%2C%20mostly-Muslim%20Palestinians.%20This%20instantly%20made%20them%20a%20natural%20compadre%20for%20the%20Hindutvavadis%2C%20who%20have%20long%20marked%20out%20Muslims%20(and%20Islam)%20as%20the%20primary%20cultural%20threat%20to%20their%20imagined%20body%20politic.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Zionist%20forces%20in%20containing%20the%20%E2%80%9CMuslim%20threat%E2%80%9D%20through%20external%20military%20aggression%20and%20internal%20colonisation%20makes%20Israel%20the%20ideal%20reference%20point%20for%20the%20Hindutva-%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evadis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20As%20Kaul%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgjia.georgetown.edu%2F2022%2F06%2F17%2Findia-israel-and-geopolitical-imaginaries-of-cooperation-and-oppression%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eobserves%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20right-wing%20majoritarian%20nationalist%20projects%20championed%20by%20the%C2%A0regimes%20in%20the%20two%20countries%C2%A0both%20portray%20themselves%20as%20beleaguered%20by%20Islamists%20and%20resolute%20in%20combating%20terrorism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20again%2C%20we%20need%20not%20hunt%20for%20clues%20in%20the%20dense%20forest%2C%20for%20the%20evidence%20sits%20bare%20in%20the%20open%20field.%20Sample%20this%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fhinduism-and-judaism-should-come-together%2Farticle29263943.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estatement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20made%20by%20senior%20BJP%20veteran%2C%20Subramaniam%20Swamy%2C%20during%20a%20joint%20panel%20discussion%20with%20Israeli%20academic%2C%20Gadi%20Taub%2C%20organised%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9CIndo-Israel%20Friendship%20Association%E2%80%9D%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20August%202019%3A%20%E2%80%9CZion%20is%20today%20under%20attack%20from%20Islamic%20extremists%2C%20and%20therefore%20both%20of%20us%20%5BHindutva-%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evadis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20Zionists%5D%20should%20come%20together%20to%20fight%20the%20Islamic%20terror%20forces.%E2%80%9D%20This%20congruence%20of%20perceived%20victimhood%20to%20Islamist%20extremism%20is%20integral%20to%20both%20ideologies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20the%20pinpoint%20identification%20of%20a%20veritable%20common%20enemy%20logically%20segues%20into%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20legal-political%20system%20that%20marginalises%20that%20enemy.%20Thus%2C%20the%20adulatory%20Hindutva%20fascination%20for%20the%20Zionist%20project%20also%20extends%20to%20its%20desire%20to%20create%20a%20hierarchical%20citizenship%20structure%20within%20a%20Hindu%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERashtra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20would%20privilege%20Hindus%20over%20other%20religious%20groups%2C%20especially%20Muslims.%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Basic%20Law%3A%20Israel%20as%20the%20Nation-State%20of%20the%20Jewish%20People%E2%80%99%20law%2C%20upheld%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202021%2C%20definitively%20establishes%20Israel%20as%20a%20homeland%20for%20Jews.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20academic%2C%20Honaida%20Ghanim%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fread.dukeupress.edu%2Fcritical-times%2Farticle%2F4%2F3%2F565%2F294168%2FIsrael-s-Nation-State-LawHierarchized-Citizenship%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eobserves%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20law%20also%20applies%20to%20Jews%20from%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20thus%20%E2%80%9C%5Breinventing%20citizenship%5D%20as%20a%20transboundary%20ethnos%20that%20automatically%20subsumes%20Jews%20from%20across%20the%20world%20into%20an%20ethnoracially%20engineered%20reserve%20of%20potential%20citizens.%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20very%20close%20to%20what%20India%E2%80%99s%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%202019%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20government%20put%20in%20place%20to%20regularise%20Hindu%20and%20five%20other%20non-Muslim%20immigrant%20groups%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan%2C%20seeks%20to%20achieve.%20The%20CAA%20iterates%20a%20certain%20breed%20of%20ethnoracial%20homelands%20politics%20that%20the%20Israeli%20%E2%80%98Basic%20Law%E2%80%99%20successfully%20institutionalised%20to%20a%20larger%20extent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENeither%20the%20Israeli%20%E2%80%98Basic%20Law%E2%80%99%2C%20nor%20the%20CAA%20(or%20even%20a%20proposed%20all-India%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens)%20are%20designed%20to%20physically%20expel%20the%20%E2%80%9Cundesirables%E2%80%9D.%20They%20are%20merely%20designed%20to%20establish%20a%20system%20of%20political%20and%20cultural%20majoritarianism%20by%20rendering%20dispensable%20groups%20into%20half-citizens%2C%20doubtful%20citizens%20or%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20non-citizens.%20In%20his%20book%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Biggest%20Prison%20on%20Earth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Pappe%20calls%20this%20unique%20formula%20of%20keeping%20the%20territories%2C%20not%20expelling%20the%20people%20in%20them%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20not%20granting%20them%20citizenship%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20unholy%20trinity%20of%20the%20consensual%20Zionist%20catechism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EVicarious%20militarism%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20the%20Hindutva%20ecosystem%E2%80%99s%20unmitigated%20fascination%20for%20the%20Israeli%20state%20and%20its%20actions%20cannot%20be%20understood%20without%20situating%20it%20in%20the%20contemporary%20context%20of%20the%20India-Israel%20bilateral%20relationship.%20Much%20has%20already%20been%20written%20about%20the%20renewed%20political%20and%20strategic%20cooperation%20between%20both%2C%20entailing%20strong%20interdependencies%20and%20investments%20in%20the%20defence%20and%20technological%20domains.%20As%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.middleeasteye.net%2Fnews%2Findia-israel-arms-trade-numbers%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMay%202022%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20journalist%20and%20writer%2C%20Assad%20Essa%2C%20shows%2C%20military-to-military%20cooperation%20between%20both%20sides%20is%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%2C%20with%20India%20emerging%20as%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20top%20arms%20buyer%20and%20key%20co-production%20partner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20of%20this%20is%20firmly%20backed%20by%20a%20longstanding%20legacy%20of%20deep%20state%20cooperation%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20eagerness%20to%20lure%20India%20away%20from%20its%20neutral%20stance%20on%20the%20Palestine%20issue%2C%20and%20more%20recently%2C%20a%20shifting%20geopolitical%20context%20in%20West%20Asia%20that%20allows%20New%20Delhi%20to%20simultaneously%20consolidate%20its%20relationship%20with%20Tel%20Aviv%20and%20the%20Arab%20monarchies%20who%20are%20themselves%20warming%20up%20to%20Israel.%20The%20revamped%20political%20and%20military%20cooperation%2C%20however%2C%20is%20merely%20a%20material%20manifestation%20of%20the%20deeper%20ideological%20intimacy%20between%20two%20ethno-racially%20driven%20regimes.%20At%20best%2C%20it%20offers%20a%20visible%20platform%20for%20both%20to%20share%20their%20imaginaries%20of%20hyper-militaristic%20nationalism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20modern%20Hindutva%20elite%2C%20especially%2C%20which%20envisions%20India%20as%20an%20assertive%20regional%20and%20global%20military%20force%2C%20Israel%20offers%20critical%20inspiration.%20Here%20is%20a%20small%20state%20that%20has%20erected%20a%20near-impenetrable%20fortress%20buttressed%20by%20formidable%20systems%20of%20deterrence%20deep%20within%20hostile%20territory.%20In%20that%20sense%2C%20the%20new%20political%20and%20security%20elite%20in%20New%20Delhi%20believes%20that%20India%2C%20which%20supposedly%20faces%20the%20spectre%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctwo-front%20war%E2%80%9D%20from%20Pakistan%20and%20China%2C%20has%20much%20to%20learn%20from%20the%20Israeli%20security%20model.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20this%20thinking%20predates%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20there%20is%20something%20new%20in%20the%20current%20security%20doctrine%20in%20Delhi%20that%20has%20strong%20echoes%20from%20the%20Israeli%20model%20%E2%80%93%20a%20leaning%20towards%20pre-emptive%20defence%2C%20also%20framed%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fstory%2Fwe-need-to-shift-to-offensive-defence%2F232027%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98offensive%20defence%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20serving%20National%20Security%20Advisor%2C%20Ajit%20Doval%20(who%20has%20played%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fmail-today%2Fstory%2Fajit-doval-national-security-advisor-india-israel-ties-strategic-ties-narendra-modi-1022229-2017-07-04%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20key%20role%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20cementing%20India-Israel%20security%20ties%20in%20recent%20years).%20The%20Uri%20surgical%20strikes%20and%20the%20Balakot%20airstrikes%20were%20both%20glaring%20manifestations%20of%20this%20new%20security%20approach%20%C3%A0%20la%20Israel%20of%20going%20deep%20inside%20enemy%20territory%20and%20taking%20out%20threats.%20More%20recently%2C%20some%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Findia-canada-diplomatic-row-justin-trudeau-narendra-modi-hardeep-singh-nijjar-8953271%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecommentators%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20drew%20positive%20comparisons%20with%20Israel%20after%20the%20Canadian%20government%20alleged%20Indian%20deep%20state%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20activist%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20in%20Vancouver%20in%20June.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fcanadian-media-trudeau-public-alleged-indian-involvement-nijjar-death%5C%22%3ECanadian%20Media%20Wonders%20Why%20Trudeau%20Went%20Public%20About%20Alleged%20Indian%20Involvement%20in%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20Death%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20top-down%20security%20doctrine%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fthe-nation%2Fthe-doval-doctrine%2Farticle23593361.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDoval%20doctrine%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20some%20call%20it%20%E2%80%93%20is%20unmistakably%2C%20at%20least%20in%20part%2C%20inspired%20from%20Israel%20and%20dovetails%20comfortably%20with%20the%20pop%20culture%20militarism%20conspicuous%20in%20the%20online%20show%20of%20solidarity%20with%20Israel.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindutva%20ecosystem%20clearly%20looks%20up%20to%20Israel%20for%20its%20militaristic%20bravado%20in%20confronting%20its%20enemies%2C%20and%20wants%20India%20to%20follow%20suit.%20But%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20much%20like%20everything%20else%20about%20the%20Hindutva-Zionism%20affair%2C%20this%20hyper-militarism%20isn%E2%80%99t%20without%20an%20ideological%20context.%20It%20is%20firmly%20underpinned%20by%20a%20shared%20sense%20of%20being%20besieged%20by%20a%20perceived%20Islamic%20threat%20manifested%20in%20the%20two%20%E2%80%98Ps%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20Palestine%20and%20Pakistan.%20So%2C%20once%20we%20scratch%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20shared%20muscularity%20between%20the%20Hindutva%20and%20Israeli%20elites%2C%20we%20find%20something%20more%20visceral%20%E2%80%93%20a%20lingering%20political%20fear%20psychosis%20that%20is%20framed%20by%20a%20deep-seated%20strategic%20paranoia%20of%20being%20under%20a%20never-ending%20state%20of%20war%20with%20the%20enemy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20all%2C%20the%20modern%20Hindutva%20ecosystem%20has%20been%20living%20its%20ethno-state%2C%20hyper-nationalistic%20dreams%20through%20the%20state%20of%20Israel.%20In%20the%20Zionist%20project%2C%20the%20modern%20Hindu%20nationalist%20elite%20sees%20a%20tangible%20conclusion%20of%20its%20own%20Hindu%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERashtra%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eblueprint.%20Israel%20shows%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20isn%E2%80%99t%20an%20abstract%20dream%3B%20that%20there%20is%20a%20step-by-step%20means%20to%20the%20end.%20What%20they%20forget%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20the%20Zionist%20project%20owes%20the%20bulk%20of%20its%20success%20to%20the%20extraordinary%20levels%20of%20financial%20assistance%20and%20committed%20political%20backing%20offered%20by%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%20in%20the%20post-war%20period.%20None%20of%20that%20is%20available%20to%20India.%20Despite%20its%20growing%20closeness%20with%20the%20West%2C%20New%20Delhi%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20enjoy%20even%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20support%20from%20the%20Western%20political%20elite%20that%20Tel%20Aviv%20does.%20This%20won%E2%80%99t%20change%20anytime%20soon.%20So%2C%20the%20Hindutva%20project%E2%80%99s%20starry-eyed%20love%20for%20Israel%20remains%20devoid%20of%20a%20real%20geopolitical%20premise%20and%20continues%20to%20operate%20on%20a%20brittle%20ideological%20fellowship.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAngshuman%20Choudhury%20is%20an%20associate%20fellow%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Research%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697085688000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F12100654%2FUntitled-design-11.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewir