%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2Fpathankot_647_010616092712.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Unidentified%20assailants%20shot%20and%20killed%20Jaish-e-Mohammed%20(JeM)%20terrorist%20Shahid%20Latif%2C%20who%20was%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20the%202016%20attack%20on%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20base%20in%20Pathankot%2C%20outside%20a%20mosque%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Sialkot%20district%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20October%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20took%20place%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Wednesday%20as%20Latif%20and%20his%20brother%20were%20leaving%20the%20Noor%20Madina%20mosque%20in%20Daska%20town%20after%20prayers%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Foct%2F11%2Fmastermind-behind-pathankot-attack-shahid-latif-shot-dead-by-unidentified-assailants-in-pakistan-2622911.html%5C%22%3Enews%20agency%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Three%20individuals%20on%20motorcycles%20opened%20fire%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20immediate%20deaths%20of%2053-year-old%20Latif%20and%20Haris%20Hashim.%20Another%20individual%20was%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20police%20officer%20of%20Sialkot%2C%20Hasan%20Iqbal%20termed%20Latif%E2%80%99s%20killing%20as%20an%20act%20of%20%E2%80%9Cterrorism%20and%20target%20killing%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CShahid%20Latif%20had%20security%20threats.%20All%20the%20investigators%20are%20on%20the%20spot.%20Details%20will%20be%20shared%20with%20media%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUPDATE%3A%3Cbr%3E%20District%20Police%20Officer%2C%20Sialkot%2C%20Hasan%20Iqbal%20has%20confirmed%20the%20killing%20of%20Shahid%20Latif%2C%20terming%20the%20incident%20as%20an%20act%20of%20%E2%80%9Cterrorism%20and%20target%20killing%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShahid%20Latif%20had%20security%20threats.%20All%20the%20investigators%20are%20on%20the%20spot.%20Details%20will%20be%20shared%20with%20media%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F3C3mpoMoP2%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F3C3mpoMoP2%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FuKcTqPs3WK%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FuKcTqPs3WK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20The%20Khorasan%20Diary%20(%40khorasandiary)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkhorasandiary%2Fstatus%2F1712062090582938105%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2011%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELatif%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Bilal%20and%20Noor%20Al%20Din%2C%20was%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20in%20India%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%20and%20served%20as%20the%20launching%20commander%20of%20Jaish-e-Mohammed%20in%20Sialkot.%20He%20was%20actively%20involved%20in%20the%20planning%2C%20facilitation%2C%20and%20execution%20of%20terror%20attacks%20in%20India%2C%20according%20to%20officials.%20Latif%20first%20entered%20Kashmir%20in%201993%20from%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20banned%20Harkat-ul-Ansar%20terror%20group.%20He%20was%20arrested%20a%20year%20later%20and%20incarcerated%20in%20the%20Kol%20Balwal%20jail%20in%20Jammu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20time%20in%20prison%2C%20it%20is%20believed%20that%20he%20was%20further%20radicalised%2C%20possibly%20by%20JeM%20chief%20Masood%20Azhar%2C%20who%20was%20also%20detained%20in%20the%20same%20facility%20until%20his%20release%20in%201999%20as%20part%20of%20the%20exchange%20for%20the%20hostages%20of%20the%20Indian%20Airlines%20plane%20that%20was%20hijacked%20and%20taken%20to%20Kandahar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20serving%2016%20years%2C%20Latif%20was%20deported%20through%20the%20Attari-Wagah%20border%20in%202010%20and%20subsequently%20reconnected%20with%20Azhar%2C%20who%20had%20by%20then%20established%20the%20JeM.%20An%20unidentified%20official%20told%20PTI%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20biggest%20blow%20to%20JeM%20on%20Pakistani%20soil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fquestions-we-must-ask-about-the-pathankot-attack%5C%22%3E2016%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Pathankot%20Air%20Force%20Station%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20seven%20IAF%20personnel%20and%20a%20three-day-long%20siege.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697040923000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2Fpathankot_647_010616092712.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-pathankot-attack-mastermind-shahid-latif-shot-dead%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shahid%20Latif%20and%20his%20brother%20were%20killed%20as%20they%20were%20leaving%20a%20mosque%20in%20Daska%20town%20of%20Sialkot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-pathankot-attack-mastermind-shahid-latif-shot-dead%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Declines%20to%20Grant%20Divorce%20to%20Couple%20in%2080s%20on%20Basis%20of%20Irretrievable%20Breakdown%20of%20Marriage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F14165452%2Fdivorce-619195_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20five-judge%20constitution%20bench%20had%20on%20May%201%20held%20in%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F37623680%2F%5C%22%3EShilpa%20Shailesh%20vs%20Varun%20Sreenivasan%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20the%20grant%20of%20divorce%20on%20the%20ground%20of%20irretrievable%20breakdown%20of%20marriage%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20right%2C%20but%20a%20discretion%20which%20is%20to%20be%20exercised%20with%20great%20care%20and%20caution.%20The%20court%20had%20declared%20that%20it%20had%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20several%20factors%20ensuring%20that%20%E2%80%98complete%20justice%E2%80%99%20is%20done%20to%20both%20parties.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20also%20held%20that%20it%20should%20be%20fully%20convinced%20and%20satisfied%20that%20the%20marriage%20is%20totally%20unworkable%2C%20emotionally%20dead%20and%20beyond%20salvation%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20dissolution%20of%20marriage%20is%20the%20right%20solution%20and%20the%20only%20way%20forward.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20court%20held%20that%20it%20has%20to%20factually%20determine%20and%20firmly%20establish%20that%20the%20marriage%20has%20irretrievably%20broken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20the%20court%20ought%20to%20consider%20several%20factors%20such%20as%20the%20period%20of%20time%20the%20parties%20had%20cohabitation%20after%20marriage%3B%20when%20the%20parties%20had%20last%20cohabited%3B%20the%20nature%20of%20allegations%20made%20by%20the%20parties%20against%20each%20other%20and%20their%20family%20members%3B%20the%20orders%20passed%20in%20the%20legal%20proceedings%20from%20time%20to%20time%3B%20cumulative%20impact%20on%20the%20personal%20relationship%3B%20whether%2C%20and%20how%20many%20attempts%20were%20made%20to%20settle%20the%20disputes%20by%20intervention%20of%20the%20court%20through%20mediation%3B%20and%20when%20the%20last%20attempt%20was%20made%2C%20etc.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20the%20period%20of%20separation%20should%20be%20sufficiently%20long%2C%20and%20anything%20above%20six%20years%20or%20more%20will%20be%20a%20relevant%20factor%2C%20it%20had%20held.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20court%2C%20however%2C%20had%20refrained%20from%20codifying%20the%20factors%20so%20as%20not%20to%20curtail%20the%20exercise%20of%20jurisdiction%20under%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F500307%2F%5C%22%3EArticle%20142(1)%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%2C%20which%20it%20held%2C%20is%20situation%20specific.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20%3Ci%3EShilpa%20Shailesh%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20the%20bench%20did%20not%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20situation%20in%20which%20one%20of%20the%20parties%20opposed%20the%20dissolution%20of%20marriage%2C%20despite%20living%20separately%20for%20many%20years.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20October%2010%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Aniriddha%20Bose%20and%20Bela%20M.%20Trivedi%2C%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20case%20in%20which%20it%20was%20satisfied%20that%20there%20was%20an%20irretrievable%20breakdown%20of%20marriage%20between%20the%20couple%2C%20but%20one%20of%20the%20spouses%20opposed%20the%20prayer%20for%20dissolution%20of%20marriage.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20wife%2C%20who%20is%2082%20years%20old%2C%20was%20willing%20to%20tend%20to%20her%20husband%2C%20who%20is%2089%2C%20despite%20living%20separately%20for%20several%20years.%20The%20wife%20had%20taken%20care%20of%20her%20three%20children%20since%201963%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20appellant-husband%20had%20exhibited%20total%20hostility%20towards%20them.%20She%20is%20still%20ready%20and%20willing%20to%20take%20care%20of%20her%20husband%20and%20does%20not%20wish%20to%20leave%20him%20alone%20at%20this%20stage%20of%20life%2C%20the%20bench%20noted.%20She%20also%20expressed%20her%20sentiments%20that%20she%20does%20not%20want%20to%20die%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98stigma%E2%80%99%20of%20being%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdivorcee%E2%80%9D%20woman.%20%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIn%20defence%20of%20marriage%20as%20an%20institution%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20agreed%20that%20in%20contemporary%20society%2C%20divorce%20may%20not%20constitute%20stigma%2C%20but%20did%20not%20want%20to%20ignore%20her%20sentiment.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20bench%20concluded%20that%20dissolving%20the%20marriage%20between%20the%20parties%20on%20the%20ground%20of%20irretrievable%20breakdown%20of%20marriage%20would%20not%20be%20doing%20%E2%80%9Ccomplete%20justice%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20parties%2C%20but%20would%20rather%20be%20doing%20injustice%20to%20the%20respondent-wife.%20The%20bench%2C%20therefore%2C%20dismissed%20the%20appeal%20of%20the%20husband%20against%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20dissolve%20the%20marriage.%20%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%20that%20the%20institution%20of%20marriage%20occupies%20an%20important%20place%20and%20plays%20an%20important%20role%20in%20society.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EDespite%20the%20increasing%20trend%20of%20filing%20divorce%20proceedings%20in%20courts%20of%20law%2C%20the%20institution%20of%20marriage%20is%20still%20considered%20to%20be%20a%20pious%2C%20spiritual%20and%20invaluable%20emotional%20life%20net%20between%20the%20husband%20and%20the%20wife%20in%20Indian%20society%2C%20the%20bench%20added.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20is%20governed%20not%20only%20by%20the%20letters%20of%20law%20but%20by%20the%20social%20norms%20as%20well%3B%20so%20many%20other%20relationships%20stem%20from%20and%20thrive%20on%20the%20matrimonial%20relationships%20in%20the%20society%2C%20the%20bench%20noted.%20%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20above%20observations%20are%20significant%2C%20especially%20as%20a%20constitution%20bench%20of%20the%20apex%20court%20is%20expected%20to%20give%20its%20verdict%20in%20the%20case%20involving%20the%20right%20of%20same-sex%20couple%20to%20marry.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20Union%20of%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Funion-government-opposes-same-sex-marriages-in-supreme-court%23%3A~%3Atext%3Dlaw-%2CUnion%2520Government%2520Opposes%2520Same%252DSex%2520Marriages%2520in%2520Supreme%2520Court%2Cthe%2520Union%2520government%2520has%2520said.%5C%22%3Eopposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20petition%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20it%20is%20against%20the%20institution%20of%20marriage%2C%20which%20it%20claimed%2C%20is%20heterosexual.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20would%20not%20be%20desirable%20to%20accept%20the%20formula%20of%20%E2%80%9Cirretrievable%20breakdown%20of%20marriage%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20straitjacket%20formula%20for%20the%20grant%20of%20relief%20of%20divorce%20under%20Article%20142%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20the%20bench%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.sci.gov.in%2Fsupremecourt%2F2009%2F13430%2F13430_2009_6_1501_47544_Judgement_10-Oct-2023.pdf%5C%22%3Econcluded%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20instant%20case%2C%20the%20bench%20agreed%20that%20there%20is%20no%20dispute%20that%20the%20parties%20have%20been%20separated%20for%20many%20years%20and%20all%20efforts%20to%20bring%20them%20together%20had%20failed.%20Under%20the%20circumstances%2C%20one%20may%20presume%20that%20the%20marriage%20is%20emotionally%20dead%20and%20beyond%20salvation%20and%20that%20there%20is%20an%20irretrievable%20breakdown%20of%20marriage%20between%20the%20parties.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20judgment%2C%20authored%20by%20Justice%20Trivedi%2C%20had%20also%20concluded%20that%20the%20appellant-husband%20had%20failed%20to%20prove%20that%20the%20respondent-wife%20had%20treated%20him%20with%20%E2%80%9Ccruelty%E2%80%9D%20or%20that%20she%20had%20%E2%80%9Cdeserted%E2%80%9D%20him%20as%20contemplated%20in%20Section%2013(1)(ia)%20and%2013(1)(ib)%20respectively%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%2C%201955.%20The%20Chandigarh%20district%20court%20had%20accepted%20the%20husband%E2%80%99s%20contention%20and%20granted%20him%20a%20divorce%2C%20which%20was%20reversed%20by%20both%20the%20single%20judge%20and%20the%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697039056000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F14165452%2Fdivorce-619195_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-divorce-irretrievable-brea