0new%20parliament%20building%20with%20great%20fanfare%20on%20the%20140%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20Vinayak%20Damodar%20Savarkar%20and%20placed%20his%20portrait%20on%20a%20pedestal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELok%20Sabha%20speaker%20and%20ministers%20paid%20handsome%20tributes%20to%20Savarkar.%20In%20the%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMann%20ki%20Baat%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20episode%20that%20followed%2C%20Modi%20serenaded%20thus%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CVeer%20Savarkar%E2%80%99s%20personality%20was%20one%20of%20strength%20and%20magnanimity.%20His%20fearless%20and%20self-respecting%20nature%20could%20not%20tolerate%20the%20mindset%20of%20slavery.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20in%20an%20article%20published%20on%20May%2026%2C%201920%2C%20in%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Young%20India%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fthe-nation%2Finterview-dr-vinay-lal-savarkar-did-very-little-for-india-independence%2Farticle64764988.ece%2Famp%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMahatma%20Gandhi%20wrote%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20under%20the%20title%2C%20%E2%80%98Savarkar%20Brothers%E2%80%99%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20these%20brothers%20have%20declared%20their%20political%20opinions%20and%20both%20have%20stated%20that%20they%20do%20not%20entertain%20any%20revolutionary%20ideas%E2%80%A6%20They%20both%20state%20unequivocally%20that%20they%20do%20not%20desire%20independence%20from%20the%20British%20connection.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20they%20feel%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20destiny%20can%20be%20best%20worked%20out%20in%20association%20with%20the%20British.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECould%20there%20be%20a%20clearer%20expression%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20Savarkar%20had%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmindset%20of%20slavery%E2%80%9D%20and%20did%20not%20want%20India%E2%80%99s%20freedom%20from%20the%20British%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20spectrum%20was%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%20(JP)%20whose%20121%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Est%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20birth%20anniversary%20falls%20on%20October%2011%2C%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F11144557%2FJayaprakash_Narayan_2001_stamp_of_India.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22946%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F11144557%2FJayaprakash_Narayan_2001_stamp_of_India.jpg%20946w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F11144557%2FJayaprakash_Narayan_2001_stamp_of_India-300x142.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-404457%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22449%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJayaprakash%20Narayan%20on%20a%202001%20stamp%20of%20India.%20Photo%3A%20Government%20of%20India%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20height%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%20movement%20in%201940%20the%20Mahatma%2C%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Viceroy%20of%20India%2C%20Lord%20Linlithgow%2C%20wrote%20this%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20arrest%20of%20Shri%20JP%20is%20unfortunate.%20He%20is%20an%20authority%20on%20socialism%E2%80%A6%20He%20is%20a%20fine%20fighter%20for%20freedom.%20He%20has%20forsaken%20all%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20deliverance%20of%20his%20country.%20His%20industry%20is%20tireless.%20His%20capacity%20for%20suffering%20is%20not%20to%20be%20excelled%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJP%E2%80%99s%20quality%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfine%20fighter%20for%20freedom%E2%80%9D%20became%20evident%20when%20the%20%E2%80%98Quit%20India%20Movement%E2%80%99%20was%20launched%20in%20August%201942%20with%20Gandhiji%20virtually%20declaring%20Independence.%20Inside%20Hazaribagh%20jail%2C%20JP%20was%20feeling%20frustrated%20in%20not%20being%20able%20to%20actively%20participate%20in%20this%20historic%20movement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20on%20the%20night%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDeepavali%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(Hindu%20festival)%20in%20November%201942%2C%20he%20along%20with%20five%20others%2C%20escaped%20the%20high-security%20jail%20by%20scaling%20a%2017-foot-high%20wall%20while%20the%20guards%20remained%20distracted%20by%20the%20festivities.%20His%20hot%20pursuit%20by%20the%20British%20%E2%80%93%20who%20placed%20a%20reward%20of%20Rs.%2010%2C000%2F-%20on%20his%20head%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20electrified%20the%20nation%20and%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement%20that%20eventually%20led%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20freedom.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETalking%20of%20freedom%2C%20in%20the%20dying%20moments%20of%20the%202nd%20millennium%2C%20standing%20on%20the%20ramparts%20of%20the%20Lincoln%20Memorial%20at%20Washington%20DC%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govinfo.gov%2Fcontent%2Fpkg%2FPPP-1999-book2%2Fhtml%2FPPP-1999-book2-doc-pg2358.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUS%20President%20Bill%20declared%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CThe%20story%20of%20the%2020th%20century%20is%20the%20triumph%20of%20freedom.%20We%20must%20never%20forget%20the%20meaning%20of%20the%2020th%20century%20or%20the%20gifts%20of%20those%20who%20worked%20and%20marched%2C%20who%20fought%20and%20died%20for%20the%20triumph%20of%20Freedom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJP%20had%20%E2%80%98worked%20and%20marched%2C%20fought%20and%20died%20for%20the%20triumph%20of%20freedom%E2%80%99%20of%20this%20country%2C%20afflicted%20with%20slavery%2C%20poverty%20and%20penury%20for%20the%20best%20part%20of%20the%2020th%20century.%20And%20he%20did%20it%20not%20once%2C%20but%20twice%20%E2%80%93%20as%20a%20fiery%20fighter%20for%20freedom%20from%20alien%20rule%20under%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20(1947)%20and%20later%20winning%20it%20back%20from%20the%20native%20%E2%80%98durbar%E2%80%99%20under%20his%20own%20stewardship%20(1977).%20This%20is%20a%20rarity%2C%20unparalleled%20in%20the%20annals%20of%20world%20history.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20in%20this%20context%20what%20eminent%20jurist%20Nani%20Palkhiwala%20wrote%20in%20his%20book%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%2C%20the%20People%3A%20India%2C%20the%20Largest%20Democracy%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ebecomes%20relevant%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6Since%20public%20memory%20is%20so%20alarmingly%20short%2C%20let%20us%20reiterate%20our%20gratitude%20to%20the%20men%20who%20suffered%20in%20diverse%20ways%20and%20whose%20sacrifices%20made%20the%20restoration%20of%20freedom%20possible.%20The%20first%20name%20that%20springs%20to%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20mind%20is%20that%20of%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan.%20Not%20since%20the%20time%20of%20Gandhiji%20has%20moral%20force%20%E2%80%93%20personified%20by%20a%20frail%20invalid%20%E2%80%93%20triumphed%20so%20spectacularly%20over%20the%20forces%20of%20evil.%20He%20changed%20decisively%20the%20course%20of%20history.%20One%20life%20transformed%20the%20destiny%20of%20620%20million.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20JP%20transformed%20the%20destiny%20of%20620%20million%20people%20in%201977.%20If%20JP%20had%20wished%2C%20he%20could%20have%20become%20the%20prime%20minister%20then.%20But%20he%20did%20not.%20Despite%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20being%20so%20keen%20that%20JP%20succeeded%20him%20as%20prime%20minister%2C%20he%20spurned%20the%20offer%20in%201964%20when%20Nehru%20passed%20away.%20Instead%2C%20he%20became%2C%20after%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20second%20liberator%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20freeing%20the%20country%20from%20the%20shackles%20of%20a%20home-brewed%20dictatorship%20imposed%20during%20the%20Emergency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fhow-the-rss-became-a-key-part-of-the-jayaprakash-narayan-movement-before-emergency%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20RSS%20Became%20a%20Key%20Part%20of%20the%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%20Movement%20Before%20Emergency%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESometimes%20leaders%20scale%20such%20lofty%20heights%20of%20national%20eminence%20that%20they%20become%20too%20big%20for%20a%20mundane%20office.%20In%20post-Independence%20India%2C%20JP%20never%20occupied%20any%20official%20seat%20of%20power%20but%20built%20abiding%20institutions%20%E2%80%93%20Socialist%20Party%2C%20Citizens%20for%20Democracy%2C%20People%E2%80%99s%20Union%20for%20Civil%20Liberties%2C%20Chatra%20Sangharsh%20Samiti%20%E2%80%93%20to%20carry%20forward%20his%20passion%20for%20freedom%20and%20fraternity.%20No%20wonder%2C%20he%20was%20regarded%20as%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20conscience%20keeper%20and%20patron%20saint.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20nations%2C%20most%20of%20all%20India%2C%20need%20an%20icon%20to%20which%20they%20can%20cleave%20when%20times%20are%20bad%2C%20and%20who%20can%20unite%20them%20across%20barriers%20of%20caste%2C%20creed%2C%20clan%20and%20language.%20The%20mid-70s%20were%20bad%20days%20and%20through%20the%20draconian%20and%20repressive%20regime%20of%20the%20Emergency%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98era%20of%20discipline%E2%80%99%20positioned%20against%20%E2%80%98anarchy%20and%20chaos%2C%E2%80%99%20Indira%20Gandhi%20was%20positioning%20herself%20as%20that%20icon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20she%20had%20succeeded%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98iconship%E2%80%99%20would%20have%20passed%20on%20to%20young%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%20who%20was%20waiting%20in%20the%20wings.%20With%20age%20in%20his%20favour%20and%20his%20known%20dislike%20for%20the%20democratic%20process%2C%20India%20would%20have%20turned%20into%20an%20autocracy.%20A%20real%20alternative%20was%20needed%20to%20prevent%20this%20tragedy%20from%20happening%20and%20JP%20with%20his%20towering%20personality%2C%20indomitable%20courage%20and%20aura%20as%20the%20hero%20of%20%E2%80%98Quit%20India%20Movement%E2%80%99%20eminently%20filled%20the%20bill%20and%20emerged%20as%20the%20icon%20of%20a%20resurgent%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20greatest%20crisis%20in%20India%20today%20is%20the%20absence%20of%20leaders%20of%20JP%E2%80%99s%20calibre.%20Hence%20the%20near-collapse%20of%20democracy%20and%20constitutional%20governance.%20There%20was%20this%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fcivilsmaterials.blogspot.com%2F2013%2F03%2Fworking-of-article-51a.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprayer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20yore%20which%20I%20used%20to%20silently%20recite%20during%20the%20dark%20days%20of%20Emergency%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CGod%2C%20Merciful%20God%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20a%20dark%20deepening%20crisis%20is%20engulfing%20this%20beloved%20land%20of%20ours%2C%20give%20us%20men%20a%20time%20like%20these%20demands%3B%20Honest%20men%2C%20men%20of%20strong%20minds%2C%20of%20big%20hearts%20and%20true%20faith%20and%20ready%20hands%3B%20Men%20whom%20the%20lust%20for%20power%20will%20not%20corrupt%3B%20Men%20whom%20the%20spoils%20of%20office%20will%20not%20buy%3B%20Men%20for%20whom%20service%20to%20the%20nation%20will%20come%20before%20their%20selves.%20Men%20who%20will%20not%20lie%3B%20Men%20who%20will%20not%20indulge%20in%20gimmickry%3B%20Men%20who%20will%20not%20feed%20us%20on%20slogans%20or%20on%20stunts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGive%20us%2C%20O%20God%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGive%20us%20men%20of%20Honour%2C%20of%20Integrity%3B%20Men%20who%20can%20and%20will%20stand%20up%20to%20demons%20of%20demagogy%3B%20Men%20who%20will%20not%20yield%20to%20treacherous%20flatterers%3B%20Men%20who%20will%20rise%20above%20the%20fog%20and%20fluff%20of%20mock%20adulation%3B%20God%2C%20give%20us%20such%20men%20as%20a%20trying%20and%20testing%20time%20like%20this%20demand.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGod%20responded%20and%20gave%20us%20JP%20who%20got%20India%E2%80%99s%20second%20freedom.%20Though%20such%20leadership%20is%20required%20much%20more%20today%2C%20god%20seems%20to%20have%20turned%20his%20back%20on%20India%2C%20and%20its%20billion-plus%20people!%20This%20is%20evident%20from%20the%20way%20JP%E2%80%99s%20ideas%20and%20ideologies%20have%20been%20betrayed%20and%20belittled%20by%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20who%20rode%20on%20his%20shoulders%20to%20capture%20power.%20This%20has%20reached%20its%20zenith%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20or%20so%20where%20Savarkar%20has%20been%20elevated%20as%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20icon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F02105634%2F0.28564200_1602392212_pm-bows-to-jayaprakash-narayan-on-his-jayanti-today.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F02105634%2F0.28564200_1602392212_pm-bows-to-jayaprakash-narayan-on-his-jayanti-today.jpg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F02105634%2F0.28564200_1602392212_pm-bows-to-jayaprakash-narayan-on-his-jayanti-today-300x134.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-611304%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22447%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20paying%20tribute%20to%20JP.%20Photo%3A%20narendramodi.in%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20a%20direct%20affront%20to%20JP%20who%20had%20trashed%20the%20vicious%2C%20communal%20and%20polarising%20agenda%20of%20%E2%80%98Hindutva%E2%80%99%20established%20by%20Savarkar%20on%20which%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20politics%20and%20governance%20survive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20attempt%20to%20equate%20India%20with%20Hindus%20and%20Indian%20history%20with%20Hindu%20history%20are%20only%20detracting%20from%20the%20greatness%20of%20India%20and%20the%20glory%20of%20Indian%20history%20and%20civilization.%20Such%20persons%2C%20paradoxical%20though%20this%20may%20seem%2C%20are%20in%20reality%20the%20enemies%20of%20Hinduism%20itself%20and%20the%20Hindus.%20Not%20only%20do%20they%20degrade%20the%20noble%20religion%20and%20destroy%20its%20catholicity%20and%20spirit%20of%20tolerance%20and%20harmony%2C%20but%20they%20also%20weaken%20and%20sunder%20the%20fabric%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20of%20which%20Hindus%20form%20such%20a%20vast%20majority%2C%E2%80%9D%20JP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsabrangindia.in%2Fcommunalism-cow-slaughter-lokanayak-jayaprakash-narayan-stood-firmly-against-rss%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20speech%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20originally%20delivered%20in%20Hindi%20at%20a%20Rashtriya%20Swayam%20Sevak%20(RSS)%20training%20camp%20in%20Patna%20on%20November%203%2C%201977.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJP%20was%20equally%20harsh%20on%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.counterview.net%2F2020%2F10%2Fjp-advised-rss-to-give-up-hindu-rashtra.html%5C%22%3Esquarely%20condemned%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%E2%80%9Chostile%20and%20alienating%20nationalism%20we%20hear%20about%20today%20which%20is%20antithetical%20to%20the%20ethos%20of%20freedom%20struggle%20and%20against%20the%20belief%20of%20all%20those%20who%20helped%20it%20evolve.%E2%80%9D%20As%20for%20RSS%2C%20he%20wanted%20it%20to%20either%20disband%20itself%20or%20give%20up%20the%20concept%20of%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20and%20adopt%20in%20its%20place%2C%20Indian%20nationhood%2C%20which%20is%20a%20secular%20concept%20and%20embraces%20all%20communities%20living%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJP%20has%20been%20facing%20criticism%20for%20providing%20a%20platform%2C%20political%20acceptance%20and%20respect%20to%20the%20RSS.%20Though%20true%2C%20this%20needs%20to%20be%20looked%20at%20from%20a%20proper%20perspective.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20Emergency%2C%20when%20he%20was%20in%20prison%2C%20JP%20wrote%20a%20letter%20addressed%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Bihar%20in%20which%20he%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Fjayaprakash-narayan-historic-blunder-bjp-rss-sangh-indira-gandhi-emergency%2F301850%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexplained%20his%20motive%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20incorporating%20them%20in%20the%20Sampoorna%20Kranti%20Andolan%20(JP%20Movement)%20I%20have%20tried%20to%20de-communalise%20them%20(RSS%20and%20Jana%20Sangh).%E2%80%9D%20The%20fact%20is%20that%20RSS%20bosses%20facing%20the%20stigma%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassination%20were%20keen%20to%20ensnare%20JP%20who%20was%20considered%20the%20champion%20of%20the%20freedom%20movement%20and%20the%20moral%20heir%20to%20the%20Mahatma.%20This%20was%20the%20strategic%20objective%20of%20the%20RSS%20and%20they%20have%20partially%20succeeded.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fhow-the-rss-betrayed-jayaprakash-narayan%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20RSS%20Betrayed%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20it%20must%20be%20remembered%20that%20JP%20was%20never%20a%20supporter%20of%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99%20communal%20agenda%20and%20politics.%20It%20was%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20deceitful%20strategies%20and%20promises%20%E2%80%93%20that%20it%20had%20accepted%20the%20aims%20of%20socialism%20and%20Sarvodaya%20%E2%80%93%20that%20undid%20JP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20had%20made%20his%20position%20clear%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fhow-the-rss-became-a-key-part-of-the-jayaprakash-narayan-movement-before-emergency%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhen%20he%20told%20Jyoti%20Basu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20or%20CPI(M)%2C%C2%A0%20in%201974%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9Cif%20you%20join%E2%80%9D%20the%20movement%20%E2%80%9Cthese%20fellows%20%5Bi.e.%2C%20the%20RSS%5D%20will%20run%20away.%E2%80%9D%20JP%20suggested%20that%20he%20had%20taken%20RSS%20on%20board%20only%20for%20pragmatic%20reasons%2C%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cour%20party%20is%20not%20there%2C%20nothing%20is%20there%2C%20and%20they%20have%20an%20organisation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHad%20Basu%20responded%20and%20the%20communists%20joined%20the%20JP%20Movement%20in%20full%20force%2C%20the%20political%20and%20economic%20landscape%20of%20India%20would%20have%20been%20vastly%20different.%20RSS%20was%20aware%20of%20this%20and%20therefore%20nursed%20a%20visceral%20hatred%20towards%20JP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20hatred%20was%20displayed%20on%20August%2012%2C%202023%20when%20the%20building%20that%20housed%20the%20Sarva%20Sewa%20Sangh%20co-founded%20by%20JP%2C%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20constituency%20of%20Varanasi%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Futtar-pradesh%2Fsarva-sewa-sangh-building-in-varanasi-demolished-2645574%5C%22%3Ewas%20brutally%20bulldozed%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20while%20it%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98sceptre%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20pampered%20zealot%20who%20%E2%80%9Cdid%20not%20want%20freedom%20from%20the%20British%E2%80%9D%20it%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98junkyard%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20forlorn%20patriot%20who%20fought%20and%20died%20for%20the%20triumph%20and%20enrichment%20of%20that%20freedom.%20Indeed%2C%20this%20is%20New%20India%20%E2%80%93%20or%20should%20I%20say%2C%20Naya%20Bharat%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fm-g-devasahayam-2%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fm-g-devasahayam-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3EM.G.%20Devasahayam%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20former%20IAS%20officer%20hailing%20from%20Kanyakumari%20district.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697032222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F09130111%2FUntitled-design-2021-02-09T130053.745.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbjp-rss-erase-jayaparakash-narayan-significance%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22JP%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20providing%20a%20platform%20and%20respect%20to%20the%20RSS.%20Though%20true%2C%20it%20must%20be%20remembered%20that%20he%20was%20never%20a%20supporter%20of%20the%20organisation's%20communal%20agenda%20and%20politics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbjp-rss-erase-jayaparakash-narayan-significance%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Satellite%20images%20show%20Gaza%20destruction%20after%20Israeli%20strikes%20-%20as%20food%20and%20water%20supplies%20dwindle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697031840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-gaza-palestine-strikes_6318124.jpg%3F20231011144610%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffrom