chools%20and%20medical%20clinics%2C%20have%20been%20damaged%20by%20airstrikes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20the%20people%20killed%20in%20Gaza%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20Relief%20and%20Works%20Agency%20for%20Palestine%20Refugees%20(UNRWA)%20found%20290%20were%20children.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.middleeasteye.net%2Fnews%2Fthey-are-all-gone-over-dozen-families-wiped-out-israeli-bombardment-gaza%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGaza%E2%80%99s%20Ministry%20of%20Health%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20said%20at%20least%2013%20entire%20families%20have%20been%20killed%20and%2060%25%20of%20people%20wounded%20are%20children%20and%20elderly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freliefweb.int%2Freport%2Foccupied-palestinian-territory%2Funrwa-situation-report-4-situation-gaza-strip-11-october-2023%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esituation%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20released%20Wednesday%2C%20UNRWA%20said%20only%2011%20out%20of%2022%20UNRWA%20health%20centers%20across%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20are%20currently%20able%20to%20provide%20primary%20healthcare%20services.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHospitals%20are%20functioning%20only%20partially%2C%E2%80%9D%20B%E2%80%99Tselem%20said.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20were%20damaged%20by%20bombing%2C%20and%20all%20are%20severely%20lacking%20medical%20equipment%20and%20fuel%20for%20electric%20generators.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENetanyahu%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98farce%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EB%E2%80%99Tselem%20also%20called%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F10%2F07%2Fmiddleeast%2Fsirens-israel-rocket-attack-gaza-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecommand%20for%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20residents%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20%E2%80%9Cleave%20now%E2%80%9D%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfarce%20with%20no%20bearing%20on%20reality.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20human%20rights%20group%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Gaza%20Strip%20is%20closed%20off%20on%20all%20sides%20and%20the%20residents%20have%20no%20way%20out.%20There%20are%20no%20shelters%20and%20no%20way%20to%20seek%20cover%20from%20airstrikes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Hamas%20militants%20rule%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20Israel%20has%20maintained%20a%20land%2C%20air%20and%20sea%20blockade%20on%20Gaza%20since%202007%20which%20is%20also%20enforced%20by%20Egypt%2C%20trapping%20over%202%20million%20Palestinians%20inside%20the%20territory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CContrary%20to%20what%20Israeli%20ministers%20are%20implying%2C%20this%20policy%20is%20not%20new%2C%20but%20has%20been%20implemented%20towards%20Gaza%20for%20many%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20B%E2%80%99Tselem%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20death%2C%20destruction%2C%20pain%20and%20horror%20it%20has%20wrought%20have%20led%20to%20nothing%20but%20more%20horror.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20part%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Ccomplete%20siege%2C%E2%80%9D%20B%E2%80%99Tselem%20said%20Israel%20has%20disconnected%20Gaza%20from%20the%20power%20grid%2C%20causing%20the%20population%20to%20rely%20on%20a%20small%20local%20power%20plant%20for%20electricity%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2023%2F10%2F1142077%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhich%20could%20run%20out%20of%20fuel%20in%20a%20few%20days%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20group%20also%20said%20water%20is%20in%20short%20supply%20and%20that%20since%20almost%20all%20water%20extracted%20in%20Gaza%20requires%20desalination%20or%20purification%20to%20drink%2C%20the%20water%20supply%20also%20relies%20on%20electricity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22HE%5C%22%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22HE%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20decision%20to%20imprison%20Gaza%20even%20more%20tightly%20than%20usual%20has%20also%20been%20implemented.%20The%20crossings%20are%20closed%20and%20goods%20cannot%20be%20brought%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20justification%20for%20these%20actions%2C%20which%20constitute%20war%20crimes%20openly%20ordered%20by%20top%20Israeli%20officials%2C%E2%80%9D%20B%E2%80%99Tselem%20said.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20in%20the%20face%20of%20horror%20and%20terror%20%E2%80%93%20intentionally%20harming%20civilians%2C%20their%20property%20and%20civilian%20infrastructure%20is%20always%20prohibited.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697027034000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F11175255%2FScreenshot-2023-10-11-at-5.52.50-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbtselem-israel-palestine-netanyahu-gaza-strip%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22B%E2%80%99Tselem%20has%20called%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20command%20for%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20residents%20to%20'leave%20now'%20a%20'farce%20with%20no%20bearing%20on%20reality.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbtselem-israel-palestine-netanyahu-gaza-strip%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rape%2C%20Harassment%20Allegations%3A%20Gujarat%20HC%20Asks%20GNLU%20To%20Reconstitute%20Fact-Finding%20Committee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F11171729%2FAdministrative_Block_at_GNLU.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Gujarat%20high%20court%20asked%20the%20Gujarat%20National%20Law%20University%20(GNLU)%20to%20reconstitute%20the%20fact-finding%20committee%20that%20is%20looking%20into%20allegations%20of%20rape%20and%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20homophobic%20atmosphere%2C%20slamming%20the%20college%E2%80%99s%20actions%20so%20far%20as%20%E2%80%9Can%20effort%20to%20cover%20up%20the%20whole%20issue%2C%20to%20save%20the%20image%20of%20the%20institution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20was%20taken%20up%20suo%20motu%20by%20the%20court%20last%20month%2C%20after%20the%3Cem%3E%20Ahmedabad%20Mirror%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper%20reported%20the%20allegations%2C%20made%20anonymously%20by%20two%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fhigh-court%2Fgujarat-high-court%2Fgujarat-high-court-rape-queer-student-harassment-gnlu-inquiry-cover-up-suo-moto-239883%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20Sunita%20Agarwal%20and%20Justice%20Aniruddha%20Mayee%20noted%20that%20the%20fact-finding%20committee%20headed%20by%20a%20retired%20IPS%20officer%2C%20Keshav%20Kumar%2C%20has%20been%20constituted%20but%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20given%20any%20report%20as%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20flagged%20its%20concern%20regarding%20the%20presence%20of%20professor%20Anjani%20Singh%20Tomar%20in%20the%20fact-finding%20committee.%20Tomar%2C%20who%20is%20the%20chairperson%20of%20GNLU%E2%80%99s%20Internal%20Complaints%20Committee%2C%20had%20already%20filed%20a%20one-line%20report%20on%20October%207%20stating%20that%20no%20student%20has%20met%20her%20or%20offered%20to%20about%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20fail%20to%20understand%20as%20to%20how%20and%20in%20what%20manner%2C%20the%20institute%20is%20dealing%20with%20the%20report%20which%20was%20published%20in%20the%20newspaper%20on%20%5BSeptember%2022%5D%2C%20more%20so%20when%20the%20intimation%20about%20such%20alleged%20incidents%20was%20received%20by%20the%20registrar%2C%20as%20per%20his%20own%20admission%2C%20on%2019%20September.%20The%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20enquiry%20is%20being%20done%20by%20the%20University%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20effort%20to%20cover%20up%20the%20whole