20Wednesday%2C%20October%2011.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20countries%2C%20India%20and%20Canada%2C%20have%20so%20far%2C%20not%20commented%20on%20the%20claims%20of%20a%20secret%20meeting%2C%20which%20would%20have%20been%20the%20highest-level%20meeting%20after%20Canadian%20prime%20minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20went%20public%20with%20his%20bombshell%20allegations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20September%2019%2C%20Trudeau%20stood%20in%20the%20lower%20house%20of%20the%20Canadian%20parliament%20and%20claimed%20that%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%20allegations%E2%80%9D%20of%20Indian%20government%20agents%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20national%2C%20whom%20New%20Delhi%20considers%20as%20a%20pro-Khalistani%20terrorist.%20India%20and%20Canada%20both%20expelled%20a%20diplomat%20each%2C%20while%20New%20Delhi%20also%20took%20the%20additional%20step%20to%20stop%20visa%20services%20for%20Canadian%20citizens.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECanadian%20foreign%20minister%20Melanie%20Joly%20had%20said%20last%20week%20that%20Ottawa%20had%20been%20in%20backroom%20talks%20with%20New%20Delhi.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20government%20of%20India.%20We%20take%20Canadian%20diplomats%E2%80%99%20safety%20very%20seriously%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20engage%20privately%20because%20we%20think%20diplomatic%20conversations%20are%20best%20when%20they%20remain%20private%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F146b4e53-07aa-4cc0-9ed7-064532fbb39c%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20a%20few%20days%20before%20Joly%20spoke%20of%20ongoing%20backroom%20talks%2C%20she%20had%20already%20met%20with%20the%20Indian%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Ja