on.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJaishankar%20addressed%20the%20diplomatic%20dispute%20for%20the%20first%20time%20on%20September%2026%20at%20an%20interactive%20discussions%20in%20Washington-based%20Council%20for%20Foreign%20Relations%20(CFR).%20%E2%80%9CWe%20told%20the%20Canadians%20that%20this%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-was-told-its-not-indias-policy-s-jaishankar-on-hardeep-singh-nijjar-killing%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enot%20the%20Government%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20policy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJaishankar%20had%20also%20reiterated%20the%20Indian%20position%20that%20New%20Delhi%20was%20willing%20to%20look%20at%20any%20specific%20information%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20there%20has%20been%20no%20official%20confirmation%20of%20any%20%E2%80%9Csecret%20meeting%E2%80%9D%2C%20Canada%20has%20continued%20to%20expand%20its%20advocacy%20for%20India%20to%20take%20the%20allegations%20seriously.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20Canadian%20prime%20minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Ftrudeau-diplomatic-spat-india-uae-president%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecalled%20up%20leaders%20of%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20and%20Jordan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20discuss%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20massive%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20in%20Israel.%20He%20also%20took%20the%20opportunity%20to%20raise%20the%20diplomatic%20dispute%2C%20asserting%20that%20India%20has%20to%20abide%20by%20the%20Vienna%20Convention%20for%20Diplomatic%20Relations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20Trudeau%20had%20pointed%20finger%20at%20India%20publicly%2C%20Canada%20had%20announced%20that%20it%20was%20going%20to%20voluntarily%20withdraw%20some%20officials%20over%20concerns%20of%20threats%20from%20social%20media.%20India%20had%20insisted%20that%20the%20exercise%20was%20initiated%20after%20New%20Delhi%20sought%20%E2%80%9Cparity%E2%80%9D%20in%20diplomatic%20presence%2C%20as%20Canada%20had%20a%20much%20higher%20number%20of%20diplomats%20stationed%20in%20the%20South%20Asian%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiplomats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EFT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20report%20also%20stated%20no%20Canadian%20diplomats%20have%20left%20India%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20India%20had%20given%20a%20deadline%20to%2041%20diplomats%20to%20leave%20by%20October%2010%2C%20noting%20that%20their%20diplomatic%20immunity%20would%20be%20revoked%20otherwise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20India%20has%20never%20announced%20this%20deadline%20for%20removal%20of%20diplomats%20publicly.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fmedia-briefings.htm%3Fdtl%2F37165%2FTranscript%2Bof%2BWeekly%2BMedia%2BBriefing%2Bby%2Bthe%2BOfficial%2BSpokesperson%2BOctober%2B05%2B2023%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20last%20week%E2%80%99s%20media%20briefing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20had%20refused%20to%20go%20%E2%80%9Cinto%20details%20of%20diplomatic%20conversations%E2%80%9D%20when%20asked%20specifically%20about%20the%20alleged%20deadline%20of%20October%2010.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20there%20is%20no%20clarity%20if%20there%20is%20any%20actual%20deadline%20which%20was%20not%20adhered%20to%20by%20the%20Canadians.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECanadian%20television%20channels%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctvnews.ca%2Fpolitics%2Fcanada-given-5-days-to-reduce-diplomatic-staff-in-india-majority-evacuated-sources-1.6590681%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECTV%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fca